We assessed similarity between pairs of gene panels across HPO terms using the Bioconductor ‘GeneOverlap’ package.42 Similarity is based on the Jacard index which is calculated by dividing the number of intersections by the number of unions:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
